[SN]TITLE[SN]
Everest trip for Newcastle schoolchildren

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A group of schoolchildren in the west end of Newcastle have been offered the chance to travel to Mount Everest base camp.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
17 July 2013 Last updated at 14:37 BST
They are training to tackle the mountainous conditions in Nepal next year.
Helen Richardson reports.
